snippet.title: Shooting Arena VR - Early Access Trailer [PC VR]
snippet.description:
Early Access trailer for Shooting Arena VR, a virtual reality arcade shooting range where you rely on speed and accuracy to become a crazy shooting expert. Developed by Infinity Studio, available for PC VR. You can find more information, as well as reviews and ratings here: https://vrgamecritic.com/game/shooting-arena-vr
